ZH: 地下水是地球上的重要水资源之一。
EN: Groundwater is one of the important water resources on Earth.

ZH: 水加工厂使用地下水来生产饮用水。
EN: Water processing plants use groundwater to produce drinking water.

ZH: 地下水通过水井抽取到地表。
EN: Groundwater is pumped to the surface through wells.

ZH: 地下水可以保持地表水的水位。
EN: Groundwater helps maintain the water level of surface water.

ZH: 污染物可能会渗入地下水，对环境造成破坏。
EN: Contaminants can seep into groundwater, causing environmental damage.

ZH: 一些植物依赖地下水来生长。
EN: Some plants rely on groundwater to grow.

ZH: 地下水层的质量受到土壤和地质的影响。
EN: The quality of groundwater is influenced by soil and geology.

ZH: 地下水可以通过蓄水层传输和储存。
EN: Groundwater can be transmitted and stored through aquifers.

ZH: 地下水资源的开采需要合理规划和管理。
EN: The exploitation of groundwater resources requires proper planning and management.

ZH: 地下水可以通过自然的过滤系统净化。
EN: Groundwater can be purified through natural filtration systems.

ZH: 地下水可以用于灌溉农田。
EN: Groundwater can be used for irrigating farmland.

ZH: 地下水的补给取决于降雨和地表径流。
EN: Groundwater recharge depends on rainfall and surface runoff.

ZH: 地下水的消耗速度可能快于补给速度。
EN: The rate of groundwater consumption may be faster than the rate of recharge.

ZH: 地下水的使用需要考虑到可持续性。
EN: The use of groundwater needs to consider sustainability.

ZH: 地下水在许多地方被过度开采。
EN: Groundwater is overexploited in many places.

ZH: 地下水是荒漠地区的重要水源之一。
EN: Groundwater is one of the important water sources in desert areas.

ZH: 地下水是一种天然的淡水资源。
EN: Groundwater is a natural freshwater resource.

ZH: 地下水对植物的生长和土壤的稳定起着重要作用。
EN: Groundwater plays an important role in the growth of plants and the stability of soil.

ZH: 地下水是地下岩石中存储的水。
EN: Groundwater is water stored in underground rocks.

ZH: 地下水的保护是保护环境和生态系统的重要举措。
EN: Protecting groundwater is an important measure to conserve the environment and ecosystem.
